OL,3,CHarry beams and Archie wears England
OL,4,Ctop in Meghan's Father's Day post
OL,6,FThe Duchess of Sussex has wished her
OL,7,Fhusband a happy Father's Day with a
OL,8,Ffamily photograph in which Prince
OL,9,FArchie is sporting an England football
OL,10,Ftop.
OL,12,FThe smiling duke is kneeling and
OL,13,Fhugging Archie and his daughter
OL,14,FPrincess Lilibet in the image posted
OL,15,Fby Meghan on Sunday.
OL,17,FIn the Instagram post, the duchess
OL,18,Fwrote: "They're so lucky to have you.
OL,19,FWe all are. Happy Father's Day to our
OL,20,Fone and only."
