OL,3,CHarry beams and Archie wears England
OL,4,Ctop in Meghan's Father's Day post
OL,6,FIn the photo, seven-year-old Archie is
OL,7,Fwearing a red and white England top
OL,8,Fwith dark blue shorts while his
OL,9,Fsister, five, has a soft toy giraffe.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FSharing the image to her stories as
OL,17,Fwell, Meghan wrote "Happy Father's
OL,18,FDay" with a white heart.
