OL,3,CHarry beams and Archie wears England
OL,4,Ctop in Meghan's Father's Day post
OL,6,FThe post comes ahead of England's next
OL,7,FWorld Cup match on Tuesday against
OL,8,FGhana.
OL,10,FThis week, speculation mounted that
OL,11,Fthe King could be reunited with the
OL,12,Fprince and princess after Harry and
OL,13,FMeghan were offered royal
OL,14,Faccommodation for their upcoming UK
OL,15,Fvisit.
OL,17,FIt is four years since Archie and
OL,18,FLilibet last saw Charles, their
OL,19,Fgrandfather, in person during Queen
OL,20,FElizabeth II's Platinum Jubilee
OL,21,Fcelebrations in 2022.
